title: Baked Honey-Lime Tilapia
ingredients: ['4 tablespoons honey', '3 tablespoons lime juice', '2 cloves garlic, finely chopped', '450g tilapia fillets', 'salt and pepper to taste', '1 butternut squash, peeled, seeded and sliced', '1 bunch fresh asparagus spears, trimmed and chopped', '1 dash chicken seasoning', '55g mozzarella cheese, grated']
